{"tid":1403895,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：拘捕暴徒可起震攝作用","createTime":"2019-08-04T00:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T00:37:31.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c022c87c8f77d6884e6d013dc23f19f671849867","tid":1403895,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:33:55.000Z","msg":"環球時報的社評指，香港警方維護法治秩序正面臨越來越大的挑戰。少數暴徒已經不將法治和作為執法主要力量的警察放在眼內，打擊這些暴徒囂張氣焰的最有效手段之一就是依法拘捕他們。<br />\n<br />\n香港法律程序複雜，但是拘捕疑犯是警察的權力，而且能够產生震攝作用。<br />\n<br />\n社評說，中央政府不會允許香港法治徹底陷落，少數暴徒能夠亂香港於一時，但絕對不能徹底顛倒香港的秩序。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察可以充分行使法律賦予的權力，對明顯施暴的示威者採取斷然措施。"},{"pid":"2f09585197165dddb43777b2459c0d29b9823d1a","tid":1403895,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:34:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1148685&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1148685%26csid%3D261_341&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvFwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=85896703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1148685&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ae73c7771e9f8e3dcf983fabf86fab7e37550880","tid":1403895,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:37:31.000Z","msg":"支那都提晒水喇，只要警察拉唔到人就無辦法震懾示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n距離出老解又近一大步，be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}